name: Oro_Dassyne
content:
Oro Dassyne was a Koorivar male warrior who led the red-armored Koorivar Fusiliers in defense of the Corporate Alliance's assets. During the Clone Wars between the Galactic Republic and the Confederacy of Independent Systems, Dassyne joined the Confederacy and fought as a general.
Oro Dassyne was first mentioned in the new Star Wars canon in Rise of the Separatists, a 2019 supplement to Fantasy Flight Games' series of Star Wars Roleplaying products. In the Star Wars Legends continuity, Oro Dassyne was introduced in the twenty-second episode of the Star Wars: Clone Wars animated series, which aired on March 25, 2005, but was only credited as "Alien General." He was later first identified in his StarWars.com Databank entry, which was published by 2006.
